                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.50 Recovery/3–2249: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister-Counselor of Embassy in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Clark</hi>
                    </persName>), <hi rend="italic">at Canton</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-03-29T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >March 29, 1949—7 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>TelCan 71. Language proposed note satisfactory Cantel 160 Mar 22. Essential this
                    be exchanged FonOff prior April 3.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
